snippet.title: What is Ikemen Go? 🤔
snippet.description:
➤ What is Ikemen Go?
IKEMEN Go is a remake of the IKEMEN (open source fighting games engine that supports M.U.G.E.N resources) in Google’s Programming Language "Go".

➤ Where to download Ikemen Go? (Scroll down to Assets)
https://github.com/Windblade-GR01/Ikemen-GO/releases

➤ Where to download LazPaint Portable?
https://portableapps.com/apps/graphics_pictures/lazpaint-portable

➤ What application do you use to record?
https://obsproject.com/

➤ Do you have a discord?
Ryon#4235
